text: Mimolaia tachira is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1992. It is known from Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Mimolaia tachira. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1992
